root: ^Yesterday, my younger brother came by the house. We were expecting him because…
^…well because we know his past present and future. We know where he is at all times and we know where he will be at any time.
^Oh.. how rude of me. We have a guest. What was your name again?
^Cecil. What a coincidence. That was my brother's name. A pleasant surprise indeed.
^I can end you in this timeline as well.
